                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200412-164-off949 t18200412-164-cd950"></join>, one saw, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200412-164-victim1607" type="victimName">
                           William 
