                  , and one other saw, value 2 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18200412-164-victim1611" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Cooper
                  <interp inst="t18200412-164-victim1611" type="surname" value="Cooper"></interp>
